<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Found it posted on May 2, 2000 right here on Maximum Eq:<BR>
<BR>
>>>Im wondering if permenant haste items fall under this rule as well. I know that the exe axe doesnt proc haste til level 30 so Im suggesting that permenant haste items like the FBSS and Mith 2H dont work until a certain level or have a reduced effect<BR>
<BR>
Permanent-haste items do not share the level restrictions of a proc on a weapon.<BR>
<BR>
-Gordon<BR>
<BR>
